## Run PostgreSQL and perform slashing protection schema migration
`cd pg;docker-compose -f ./docker-compose-pg.yml up`

## Run Web3Signer with slashing protection enabled
`cd web3signer;docker-compose -f ./docker-compose-web3signer.yml up`

## Stop or shutdown containers completely:
docker-compose -f ./docker-compose-web3signer.yml stop | down -v
docker-compose -f ./docker-compose-pg.yml [stop | down -v]

